{"tid":342705,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【侵侵又炒人】上任不足兩周 白宮傳訊總監被特朗普炒魷","createTime":"2017-07-31T22:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T09:53:18.000Z","uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ff05e2d0fd9d71c35c2cd3029bc094e23462bc","tid":342705,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T22:42:31.000Z","msg":"【侵侵又炒人】上任不足兩周 白宮傳訊總監被特朗普炒魷<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170801&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57026293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170801%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57026293&d=Tn%2F0yZDUumzN1QvX0F5%2FI8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=085d6842\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170801%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57026293&h=1f14483f\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170801&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57026293</a><br />\n<br />\n上任僅11天的白宮傳訊總監斯卡拉穆奇（Anthony Scaramucci），周一被總統特朗普炒魷。<br />\n<br />\n白宮解釋，特朗普認為斯卡拉穆奇在訪問中的言論不恰當，又指他在政府中再無任何職務。白宮又表示，斯卡拉穆奇離職，令周一履新的白宮幕僚長凱利（John Kelly)可「重整旗鼓」。<br />\n<br />\nPolito網站引述消息，指特朗普是應凱利要求，炒掉斯卡拉穆奇。特朗普上周委任國土安全部長凱利接替普里伯斯（Reince Priebus）的白宮幕僚長職務，令上任僅189日的普里伯斯成為美國近代史上最「短命」幕僚長。<br />\n<br />\n53歲的斯卡拉穆奇（Anthony Scaramucci）是特朗普的金融界好友，上月獲委任為白宮傳訊總監後，觸發上任六個月的白宮發言人斯派塞（Sean Spicer）辭職。據報斯卡拉穆奇的任命是特朗普跟家人的決定，令斯派塞感到被侮辱，亦令普里伯斯及首席智囊班農極為不滿。<br />\n<br />\n斯卡拉穆奇上周接受傳媒訪問時，用粗口炮轟普里伯斯和總統首席智囊班農，又揚言會炒掉所有不聽話的人。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》／美聯社／路透社"},{"pid":"693071ca978dffb7cdfd980bc15bdc7bc41a3065","tid":342705,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T22:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc8d8fdf5c04e7a8c301e3099fccb623705ec6f","tid":342705,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:04:00.000Z","msg":"呢個位應該可有可無。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉黎轉去都無影響白宮運作"},{"pid":"07f203f4e6931f5b09387c854cab5e26a39e991f","tid":342705,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個位應該可有可無。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉黎轉去都無影響白宮運作</blockquote><br />\n個低能侵自己係twitter打字咪得囉"},{"pid":"a29eaddee1597362ce9897cc1fae7d9bade8863d","tid":342705,"uid":19889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:06:04.000Z","msg":"管理公司方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b91fa1de94184680399cb2cc6659eaa7babd1c","tid":342705,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:17:30.000Z","msg":"侵侵：you are fired<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8de6e3d2af1ac612d1068566544c5e2e37a670","tid":342705,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:33:17.000Z","msg":"上任十日，老婆申請離婚，跟手畀人炒埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170801/20108360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170801%2F20108360&d=Tn%2F0yZDUumzN1QvX0F5%2FI8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=3e50f286\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170801%2F20108360&h=6ff0610a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170801/20108360</a>"},{"pid":"f4da0cecbdeb4693f706480f7b95eb5907edba02","tid":342705,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1ff2a01e28d52a5602ce0792739bb3d71d2de8","tid":342705,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上任十日，老婆申請離婚，跟手畀人炒埋